<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This Standard is promulgated based on Paragraph 1 of Article 10 of the Charges and Fees Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Museum provides the Auditorium and its facilities to the public at charges and fees based on this Standard. The charges and fees are itemized as shown in the attached table.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The charges and fees must be paid in full by the Applicant no less than fifteen days prior to the starting day of the event. Overtime usage will be subject to overtime charges as itemized in the attached table and must be paid in full no less than seven days following the closing day of the event.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The Applicant must return the site and facilities item by item after use.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The charges and fees will be reviewed at least once every three years according to changes in cost, administration fees, and consumer price index.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[This standard shall be effective immediately upon date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
